title: Cynthia Lummis
added: In January 2021, Lummis joined a group of Republican senators (led by Ted Cruz) attempting to overturn the results of the presidential election by announcing they would refuse to certify the votes of the Electoral College. Accordingly, on January 6, Hyde-Smith voted in support of the objection to the electoral vote for Pennsylvania. The Senate rejected this objection by 92-7.
